  "title": "King of the Hill",
  "description": "Grindstone’s King of the Hill is back! Each show, a cast of improvisers hash it out in this comedy battle royale! Our improvisers use audience suggestions to create unique characters, scenes and sketches on the spot. After each round, our audience votes, knocking out the bottom performers until we crown a reigning monarch!",
